 《命运2》开发商承诺在裁员和延期消息传出后恢复“信任” https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/destiny-2-developer-pledges-to-restore-trust-after-news-of-layoffs-and-delays-3530128?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=命运 2 开发商承诺在裁员和延迟消息传出后恢复信任Imogen DonovanFri, 03 Nov 2023 13:27:31 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPCPS4PS5Xbox OneXbox Series SXbox Series X https://www.nme.com/?p=3530128 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/destiny-2-doesnt-matter-anymore-say-fans-after-layoffs.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/destiny-2-doesnt-matter-anymore-say-fans-after-layoffs.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/destiny-2-doesnt-matter-anymore-say-fans-after-layoffs-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/destiny-2-doesnt-matter-anymore-say-fans-after-layoffs-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/destiny-2-doesnt-matter-anymore-say-fans-after-layoffs-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/destiny-2-doesnt-matter-anymore-say-fans-after-layoffs-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/destiny-2-doesnt-matter-anymore-say-fans-after-layoffs-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “这是我们工作室历史上最困难的几周之一”</p><p> 《命运 2》的开发商在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>首先报道了<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/destiny-2-developer-pledges-to-restore-trust-after-news-of-layoffs-and-delays-3530128">裁员和延期的消息后，承诺恢复“信任”</a> 。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/destiny-2-doesnt-matter-anymore-say-fans-after-layoffs.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/destiny-2-doesnt-matter-anymore-say-fans-after-layoffs.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/destiny-2-doesnt-matter-anymore-say-fans-after-layoffs-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/destiny-2-doesnt-matter-anymore-say-fans-after-layoffs-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/destiny-2-doesnt-matter-anymore-say-fans-after-layoffs-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/destiny-2-doesnt-matter-anymore-say-fans-after-layoffs-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/destiny-2-doesnt-matter-anymore-say-fans-after-layoffs-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/destiny-2"><em>《命运 2》</em></a>的开发商承认，在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/destiny-2-fans-worry-that-the-game-doesnt-matter-anymore-after-layoffs-3526713">宣布裁员</a>和可能推迟新资料片后，他们“失去了很多[玩家]信任”。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/best-upcoming-games-we-saw-at-gamescom-2023-3505950">以下是我们在 Gamescom 2023 上看到的一些即将推出的最佳游戏</a></strong></li></ul><p>“这是我们工作室历史上最困难的几周之一，” <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/bungie">Bungie</a>在其官方网站上<a href="https://www.bungie.net/7/en/News/article/ourpathforward" target="_blank" rel="noopener">发帖</a>称。</p><p> 10月30日，首席执行官皮特·帕森斯(Pete Parsons)证实<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/halo-and-destiny-composer-michael-salvatori-apparently-laid-off-from-bungie-3526667">开发商出现亏损</a>，但没有具体说明具体数字和部门。独立分析师将此归因于<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/playstation">PlayStation</a>的更广泛“重组”，Bungie 是该公司的子公司。 </p><figure id="attachment_3526705" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3526705" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3526705" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/destiny-2-composer-caught-in-layoffs.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/destiny-2-composer-caught-in-layoffs.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/destiny-2-composer-caught-in-layoffs-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/destiny-2-composer-caught-in-layoffs-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/destiny-2-composer-caught-in-layoffs-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/destiny-2-composer-caught-in-layoffs-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/destiny-2-composer-caught-in-layoffs-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3526705" class="wp-caption-text"> 《命运 2》图片来源：Bungie</figcaption></figure><p> “这一周我们一直在互相支持，包括那些在工作室的人，以及不再在工作室的朋友和同事，”Bungie 继续说道。</p><p>此外，<em>彭博社</em>本周发布了一份报告，声称资料片<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/destiny-2-fans-think-paul-mccartney-is-coming-back-for-a-new-soundtrack-3473012"><em>《The Final Shape》</em></a>将于 2024 年 6 月而不是 2024 年 2 月发布。</p><p>在这篇文章中，Bungie 并未承认这一说法，并分享了其“让<em>The Final Shape</em>成为令人难忘的<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/destiny"><em>《命运》</em></a>体验”的雄心。</p><p> “我们希望打造一款能够与我们曾经制作过的最佳游戏并驾齐驱的游戏——一个恰当的顶峰，以纪念我们过去十年共同经历的旅程。 <em>《遗落之族》、《女巫女王》</em>和<em>《被掳之王</em>》——这些是我们力争实现的目标。” </p><figure id="attachment_3526776" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3526776" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3526776" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/destiny-2-doesnt-matter-anymore-say-fans-after-layoffs-3.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/destiny-2-doesnt-matter-anymore-say-fans-after-layoffs-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/destiny-2-doesnt-matter-anymore-say-fans-after-layoffs-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/destiny-2-doesnt-matter-anymore-say-fans-after-layoffs-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/destiny-2-doesnt-matter-anymore-say-fans-after-layoffs-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/destiny-2-doesnt-matter-anymore-say-fans-after-layoffs-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/destiny-2-doesnt-matter-anymore-say-fans-after-layoffs-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3526776" class="wp-caption-text"> 《命运 2》图片来源：Bungie</figcaption></figure><p>因此，仍在支持《命运 2》及其未来的 650 名员工正在“倾注全部精力和专业知识来交付这一史诗般的时刻及其后续剧集”。</p><p>然而，<em>彭博社</em>最近的一份<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-10-31/sony-s-bungie-game-unit-cut-jobs-as-destiny-2-popularity-waned?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzb3VyY2UiOiJTdWJzY3JpYmVyR2lmdGVkQXJ0aWNsZSIsImlhdCI6MTY5ODc4Mjc3OSwiZXhwIjoxNjk5Mzg3NTc5LCJhcnRpY2xlSWQiOiJTM0VQTFFEV0xVNjgwMSIsImJjb25uZWN0SWQiOiJGRUIzODlCNUI2ODI0RTY0QjY5MENEODE1RTBDREZGRCJ9.8iJtSlPe7GT5nO9_xgcUM9kIIEWKcZskdkj539g7ooo">报告</a>称，那些失业的人只是收到了“安排在他们日历上的神秘的 15 分钟会议”的通知。</p><p>社区管理和出版等显然在裁员中受到打击的部门现在将被外包。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，<em>收获日 3 的</em>最新补丁<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/payday-3-patch-1-0-1-rolls-out-a-lot-of-minor-fixes-across-all-platforms-3530089">解决了游戏中的许多问题</a>，例如控制器兼容性、崩溃、版本独占等。</p><p> 《命运 2》的开发商在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>首先报道了<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/destiny-2-developer-pledges-to-restore-trust-after-news-of-layoffs-and-delays-3530128">裁员和延期的消息后，承诺恢复“信任”</a> 。</p> ;
观看彼得·杰克逊执导的披头士乐队“最后”歌曲“Now And Then”的音乐视频https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-peter-jackson-directed-music-video-the-beatles-final-song-now-and-then-3530133?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=watch-彼得·杰克逊执导的披头士乐队最后一首歌的音乐视频Liberty DunworthFri, 03 Nov 2023 13:00:02 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNewsPopRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3530133 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Beatles@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="披头士乐队 1962 年澳大利亚巡演后抵达伦敦" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Beatles@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Beatles@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Beatles@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Beatles@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Beatles@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Beatles@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>它包含最近出土的披头士四人组的镜头</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-peter-jackson-directed-music-video-the-beatles-final-song-now-and-then-3530133">观看由彼得·杰克逊执导的披头士乐队“最后”歌曲《Now And Then》的音乐视频，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Beatles@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="披头士乐队 1962 年澳大利亚巡演后抵达伦敦" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Beatles@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Beatles@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Beatles@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Beatles@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Beatles@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Beatles@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-beatles">披头士乐队</a>“最后”歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-beatles-final-song-now-and-then-3529039">“Now And Then”</a>的新音乐视频已被分享，由彼得·杰克逊执导，并以新出土的成员镜头为特色。看看下面。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/the-beatles-now-and-then-final-song-ai-documentary-peter-jackson-music-video-inside-story-3527104">“现在和那时”的内部：在人工智能的一点帮助下，披头士乐队再次复活</a></strong></li></ul><p>经过几个月的炒作，这首新歌被乐队称为最后一首由四位原成员参与的单曲，于昨天（11 月 2 日）发布。</p><p>这个备受期待的项目名为“Now And Then”， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-mccartney-says-artificial-intelligence-has-enabled-a-final-beatles-song-3455297">早在六月份就被麦卡特尼首次调侃，</a>当时他确认他正在与鼓手合作创作一首新曲目。</p><p>它源自已故乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/john-lennon">约翰·列侬</a>录制的演示磁带，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-mccartney-says-artificial-intelligence-has-enabled-a-final-beatles-song-3455297">在人工智能的帮助下完成</a>，这将歌曲作者的声音从最初的录音中剔除出来，并允许幸存的成员与他们一起工作。</p><p>现在，继<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-beatles-final-song-now-and-then-3529039">昨天这首歌终于揭晓</a>—— <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liverpools-jacaranda-club-hosts-emotional-beatles-listening-party-for-now-and-then-3529240">歌迷们对最终结果感到激动不已</a>——乐队今天分享了音乐视频。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/peter-jackson-to-direct-music-video-for-final-beatles-song-using-newly-unearthed-footage-3526878">正如本周早些时候宣布的那样</a>，《Now And Then》的视觉伴奏由著名电影制作人彼得·杰克逊执导，其中包括一些令人难以置信的披头士四人组的存档镜头。</p><p>看看下面。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="披头士乐队 - 现在和那时" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Opxhh9Oh3rg?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>该项目是与<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/apple">Apple Corps Ltd.</a> 、Capitol 和 UMe 合作制作的，是该电影制片人制作的第一部音乐视频，也是他与乐队在 2021 年纪录片系列<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/the-beatles-get-back-review-3103706">《披头士乐队：回归》</a></em>中合作的延续。</p><p>在本周早些时候分享的一份新闻稿中，杰克逊详细说明了他不愿意承担为“最后”歌曲制作视觉效果的艰巨任务，并表示他发现“一系列的焦虑几乎难以应对”。</p><p>他还表示，他试图以缺乏乐队的相关镜头为借口来回避这项任务——因为他收到了 1995 年新出土的 14 个小时的成员在一起的镜头。</p><p>最终结果中还嵌入了幸存成员参与该项目的新镜头，杰克逊后来表示他完全拒绝在音乐视频中使用任何 CGI 镜头，并表示“披头士乐队的每个镜头都必须是真实的”。</p><p>除了与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-mccartney">麦卡特尼</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ringo-starr">林戈·斯塔尔</a>合作开展该项目外，杰克逊还获得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/john-lennon">约翰·列侬</a>的儿子肖恩和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/george-harrison">乔治·哈里森</a>的妻子奥利维亚的帮助，他们各自为他的项目提供了“一些精彩的未曾见过的家庭电影片段”。还嵌入了由皮特·贝斯特 (Pete Best) 提供的“披头士乐队最早的已知电影”的一些内容，展示了四人穿着皮衣的表演。 </p><figure id="attachment_3530144" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3530144" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3530144" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Beatles1@2000x1270.jpg" alt="披头士乐队在后台摆出一张早期集体照，（从左到右）林戈·斯塔尔、乔治·哈里森、约翰·列侬（吹口琴）、保罗·麦卡特尼，1962 年" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Beatles1@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Beatles1@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Beatles1@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Beatles1@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Beatles1@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Beatles1@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3530144" class="wp-caption-text">披头士乐队在后台摆出一张早期集体照，（左）林戈·斯塔尔、乔治·哈里森、约翰·列侬（演奏口琴）、保罗·麦卡特尼，1962 年。图片来源：Harry Hammond/V&amp;A Images/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>在他的声明中，制片人确认该项目是在 Jabez Olssen 的帮助下完成的，他也参与了<em>《归来》</em>系列纪录片的制作，哈里森的儿子 Dhani 也参与了音乐视频的制作，以帮助捕捉正确的内容。气氛。</p><p> “我意识到我们需要每个观众的想象力来做我们做不到的事情，并让每个观众创造他们自己的告别披头士乐队的时刻，”杰克逊解释道。</p><p> “幸运的是，达尼·哈里森（Dhani Harrison）恰巧此时正在新西兰访问。我和他讨论了结局，并描述了我一直在考虑的一个模糊的想法。他的眼睛立刻充满了泪水——所以我们就这样走了。”</p><p>如前所述，这首歌曲的基础源自约翰·列侬在 70 年代末仅用钢琴和人声创作和录制的想法。 1994 年，他的遗孀<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yoko-ono">小野洋子</a>将这张唱片送给了麦卡特尼、哈里森和斯塔尔。 </p><figure id="attachment_3530141" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3530141" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3530141" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Beatles2@2000x1270.jpg" alt="披头士乐队于 1967 年 5 月 19 日在伦敦教堂街 24 号布莱恩·爱泼斯坦 (Brian Epstein) 的家中出席新专辑《佩珀中士的孤独之心俱乐部乐队》的新闻发布会" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Beatles2@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Beatles2@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Beatles2@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Beatles2@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Beatles2@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Beatles2@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3530141" class="wp-caption-text">披头士乐队于 1967 年 5 月 19 日在伦敦教堂街 24 号布莱恩·爱泼斯坦 (Brian Epstein) 的家中举行新专辑《佩珀中士的孤独之心俱乐部乐队》新闻发布会。图片来源：John Downing/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>斯塔尔后来与 Macca 一起参与了这个项目，他后来透露，听到演示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ringo-starr-says-making-final-beatles-song-was-like-having-john-lennon-back-3526791">让他感觉约翰·列侬又回到了</a>他们身边，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ringo-starr-last-beatles-song-created-with-ai-beautiful-track-3469906">形容最终的结果“很漂亮”</a> 。他们还用<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/are-the-beatles-teasing-the-release-of-their-final-song-3521300">社交媒体和互联网上发布的盒式磁带图像</a>以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-beatles-continue-to-tease-final-song-with-projections-across-liverpool-3521832">披头士四人家乡利物浦</a>的投影来调侃这首单曲。</p><p>周三（11 月 1 日）， <em>The One Show</em>和乐队的 YouTube 频道还播放了一部情感<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-beatles-short-film-now-and-then-the-last-beatles-song-3528193">短片</a>，记录了这首歌曲背后的历史以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-mccartney-kept-now-and-then-a-secret-from-session-musicians-we-couldnt-tell-them-it-was-a-new-beatles-song-3529048">它是如何组合在一起的</a>。</p><p>接下来， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-beatles-final-ai-song-now-and-then-blue-red-album-reissues-trailer-documentary-3522051">披头士乐队将于下周五（11 月 10 日）发行立体声和杜比混合的《1962-1966（红色专辑）》和《1967-1970（蓝色专辑）》的新扩展版本</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-peter-jackson-directed-music-video-the-beatles-final-song-now-and-then-3530133">观看由彼得·杰克逊执导的披头士乐队“最后”歌曲《Now And Then》的音乐视频，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
