 《收获日 3》补丁 1.0.1 在所有平台上推出了许多“小修复” https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/payday-3-patch-1-0-1-rolls-out-a-lot-of-minor-fixes-across-all-platforms-3530089？ utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=payday-3-patch-1-0-1-在所有平台上推出大量次要修复Imogen DonovanFri, 03 Nov 2023 12:28:09 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPCPS5Xbox Series SXbox Series XXbox Series X|S https://www.nme.com/?p=3530089 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/payday-3-patch-out-now.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/payday-3-patch-out-now.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/payday-3-patch-out-now-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/payday-3-patch-out-now-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/payday-3-patch-out-now-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/payday-3-patch-out-now-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/payday-3-patch-out-now-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>以及抢劫模拟器的下一步</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/payday-3-patch-1-0-1-rolls-out-a-lot-of-minor-fixes-across-all-platforms-3530089">《Payday 3》补丁 1.0.1 发布后，在所有平台上推出了许多“小修复”，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/payday-3-patch-out-now.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/payday-3-patch-out-now.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/payday-3-patch-out-now-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/payday-3-patch-out-now-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/payday-3-patch-out-now-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/payday-3-patch-out-now-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/payday-3-patch-out-now-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/starbreeze">Starbreeze</a>已在所有平台上发布了<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/payday-3"><em>Payday 3</em></a> 1.0.1 补丁，其中包含抢劫模拟器的更改和修复列表以及对未来的意图。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/avatar-frontiers-of-pandora-preview-far-cry-james-cameron-3522152">《阿凡达：潘多拉边境》为詹姆斯·卡梅隆的史诗片增添了“孤岛惊魂”的元素</a></strong></li></ul><p>“经历了一些不稳定之后，我们终于恢复正常运行了！抢劫犯抢劫，平民尖叫，警察陷入困境！我们还有更多烹饪内容，当您发现错误时请随时告诉我们并向我们发送您的建议！”开发者在向 Steam 发布的<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/1272080/view/3775765476417960173?l" target="_blank" rel="noopener">公告</a>中说道。</p><p>修复内容包括向正确的玩家重新发布预购和版本内容、切换<em>《收获日 3</em> 》语言的能力、与无线电、跳马、爆炸以及 PC 上 PS5 控制器的瞄准辅助相关的崩溃。 </p><figure id="attachment_3530112" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3530112" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3530112" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/payday-3-patch-out-now-3.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/payday-3-patch-out-now-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/payday-3-patch-out-now-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/payday-3-patch-out-now-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/payday-3-patch-out-now-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/payday-3-patch-out-now-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/payday-3-patch-out-now-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3530112" class="wp-caption-text"> 《收获日 3》出处：Deep Silver</figcaption></figure><p>该补丁旨在解决一些“小问题”，但“装甲升级”和“最后一人站立”将在“下一个大补丁”中得到解决。</p><p> “除了这两个技能之外，我们预计下一个补丁中不会对技能进行任何重大削弱，但考虑到玩家仍在适应游戏，我们将密切关注元数据，”Starbreeze 继续说道。</p><p>此外，装甲将成为计划在明年推出的另一系列更新的目标。完整的补丁说明可以<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/1272080/view/3775765476417960173?l" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>阅读。</p><p> <em>《收获日 3》</em> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/payday-3-developer-apologises-for-nightmare-server-issues-at-launch-3503549">自推出以来一直举步维艰</a>，其服务器存在重大问题，而且 PS5 上的主机版本不正确。 </p><figure id="attachment_3530114" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3530114" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3530114" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/payday-3-patch-out-now-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/payday-3-patch-out-now-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/payday-3-patch-out-now-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/payday-3-patch-out-now-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/payday-3-patch-out-now-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/payday-3-patch-out-now-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/payday-3-patch-out-now-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3530114" class="wp-caption-text"> 《收获日 3》出处：Deep Silver</figcaption></figure><p> “虽然不可能为每种情况做好准备，但我们应该能够做得更好，”首席执行官 Tobias Sjögren 说道。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/call-of-duty-modern-warfare-3-gross-xbox-startup-screen-criticised-by-players-3530006">提示 Xbox 用户购买<em>《使命召唤：现代战争 3》的</em>弹出窗口</a>遭到了玩家的贬低：“我知道选择退出按钮很容易，但这感觉很恶心。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/payday-3-patch-1-0-1-rolls-out-a-lot-of-minor-fixes-across-all-platforms-3530089">《Payday 3》补丁 1.0.1 发布后，在所有平台上推出了许多“小修复”，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
